Koga Shuko/Serpentor/Shockwave:


Serpentor looked to Cyber Claw with a lopsided grin.  "Riiiiight.  I ain't 
done yet you Autobot piece o-AIIIIIIIIIIEEEEE!" Serpentor screamed, his body 
flying backwards, smashing through a tree, his left arm blown off.


A purple fighter flew overhead, firing twenty rapid lasers down at Cyber 
Claw, launching a missile off at Shuko.  

Shuko saw Shockwave's missile come, but to late.  The missile sent him flying 
backwards through the air, slamming to the ground as the rogue jet flew 
overhead.
